# Move windows using numpad keys
Key KP_Home             A $[Mod2] Window-MPAnimatedMove w-100p	w-100p
Key KP_Up               A $[Mod2] Window-MPAnimatedMove w0p	w-100p
Key KP_Page_Up          A $[Mod2] Window-MPAnimatedMove w100p 	w-100p
Key KP_Left             A $[Mod2] Window-MPAnimatedMove w-100p	w0p
Key KP_Begin            A $[Mod2] -
Key KP_Right            A $[Mod2] Window-MPAnimatedMove w100p	w0p
Key KP_End              A $[Mod2] Window-MPAnimatedMove w-100p	w100p
Key KP_Down             A $[Mod2] Window-MPAnimatedMove w0p	w100p
Key KP_Page_Down        A $[Mod2] Window-MPAnimatedMove w100p	w100p

# vim:ft=fvwm
